the principal now.

00:03:09,322 --> 00:03:10,991
Phil Anderson.

00:03:11,057 --> 00:03:12,859
He's certainly had
his hands full this semester.

00:03:12,926 --> 00:03:14,327
STOKES:
Oh, yeah, that's right,

