00:04:33,964 --> 00:04:36,299
Aw, David, suck it up.

00:04:37,367 --> 00:04:39,870
There he is.

00:04:44,675 --> 00:04:47,277
Yep, he's dead.

00:04:47,344 --> 00:04:50,681
David, you think
you have a hard job?

00:04:50,747 --> 00:04:53,884
Well, Officer, I am
the one who has to
haul him out of here.

00:04:53,950 --> 00:04:55,252
WILLOWS:
Unlock the cuffs.

00:04:55,318 --> 00:04:56,420
OFFICER:
Got it.

